{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a hazy view of the Golden Gate Bridge and Alcatraz Island in San Francisco. Three military aircraft are flying in formation above the bridge, adding a dynamic element to the landscape. The bridge stretches across the water, its iconic red-orange color softened by the fog. Alcatraz Island sits prominently in the foreground, surrounded by choppy water with several small boats scattered around. The distant hills and shoreline are barely visible through the mist, contributing to a slightly muted, atmospheric quality. The overall impression is one of scale and historical significance.",
